Permissions
r - stands for reading permission
w - write permission
x - execute permission

Numeric notation for chmod
Ex: 755
Owner (7): Read(4) + Write(2) + Execute(1) = 7
Group (5): Read(4) + Execute(1) = 5
Others (5): Read(4) + Execute(1) = 5

Symbolic Notation for chmod
Ex: u+x
u (Owner)
g (Group)
o (Others) 
a (All)
A "+" adds permission and a "-" removes permission
